p:
Recall@K (가장 중요):
\text{Recall@K} = \frac{1}{|\mathcal{U}_{\text{test}}|}
\sum_{u \in \mathcal{U}_{\text{test}}}
\frac{|\mathcal{R}_u^K \cap \mathcal{G}_u|}{|\mathcal{G}_u|}

NDCG@K (rank-aware):
\text{NDCG@K} = \frac{1}{|\mathcal{U}_{\text{test}}|}
\sum_{u} \frac{\text{DCG@K}_u}{\text{IDCG@K}_u},
\quad
\text{DCG@K}_u = \sum_{i=1}^{K}
\frac{\mathbb{1}[r_u(i) \in \mathcal{G}_u]}{\log_2(i+1)}

MRR (가장 첫 hit 의 역수):
\text{MRR} = \frac{1}{|\mathcal{U}_{\text{test}}|}
\sum_{u} \frac{1}{\text{rank}(\text{first hit in } \mathcal{R}_u)}

ol.li:
학습된 Two-tower 의 item embedding 을 사용해, brute-force
   torch.matmul 로 exact top-K 정답 집합 \mathcal{R}_u^{K,\star}
   를 한 번 계산하고 캐시한다.

ac:structured-macro.ac:plain-text-body:
concurrency ∈ {1, 4, 16, 64}
warmup: 1000 query (결과 폐기)
measure: 30 초간 가능한 만큼 (또는 최소 10000 query)

\text{IsoRecallCostRatio}_{R=r}
= \frac{\$/\text{QPS}\,|\, \text{baseline at Recall@K vs exact} = r}
       {\$/\text{QPS}\,|\, \text{VDPU at Recall@K vs exact} = r}
